title: NOTICE: Oregon Law prohibits the re-sale of older, unsafe
text:
NOTICE: Oregon Law prohibits the re-sale of older, unsafe ad date: 10/07/2015 
NOTICE: Oregon Law prohibits the re-sale of older, unsafe baby cribs by private parties. For more info. about the crib you want to sell or buy, call the Consumer Product Safety Commission at 800-638-2772
